# Generated outputs policy:
# - This repo must not ship or commit tool-generated outputs.
# - Keep ignores conservative (do not ignore broad game asset paths like meshes/ or textures/).

## Common generator output folders (when someone accidentally points a tool at the repo)
**/DynDOLOD_Output/
**/TexGen_Output/
**/xLODGen_Output/
**/GrassCache/
**/ShaderCache/
**/Overwrite/
**/overwrite/

## Common xEdit backup folders (transient)
**/SSEEdit Backups/
**/TES5Edit Backups/

## Diagnostics artifacts (never ship)
**/Crash Logs/
**/NetScriptFramework/
*.log
*.dmp

## Optional: if you use the recommended MO2 output mod naming, ignore those directories too
mods/VR - Output - */

